### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ============ AUTH ============

### Registrar usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Dados do usuário autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ AUTHORS ============

### Listar autores (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/authors

### Buscar autor por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/authors/ID_DO_AUTOR

### Criar autor (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/authors
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Machado de Assis",
  "bio": "Maior escritor da literatura brasileira"
}

### Atualizar autor (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/authors/ID_DO_AUTOR
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "Escritor e poeta brasileiro do séc. XIX"
}

### Deletar autor (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/authors/ID_DO_AUTOR
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ BOOKS ============

### Listar livros (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books

### Buscar livro por ID (inclui autor, empréstimos e reservas)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/ID_DO_LIVRO

### Criar livro (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dom Casmurro",
  "isbn": "978-85-359-0277-5",
  "year": 1899,
  "synopsis": "Clássico da literatura brasileira",
  "authorId": "ID_DO_AUTOR"
}

### Atualizar livro (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/ID_DO_LIVRO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "synopsis": "Nova sinopse"
}

### Deletar livro (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/ID_DO_LIVRO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ LOANS ============

### Listar empréstimos
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar empréstimo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/ID_DO_EMPRESTIMO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar empréstimo
POST {{baseUrl}}/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "ID_DO_LIVRO",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-30T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Devolver livro (dono ou ADMIN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/loans/ID_DO_EMPRESTIMO/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Deletar empréstimo (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/loans/ID_DO_EMPRESTIMO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ RESERVATIONS ============

### Listar reservas
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar reserva por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_DA_RESERVA
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar reserva
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "ID_DO_LIVRO"
}

### Confirmar reserva (ADMIN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_DA_RESERVA/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancelar reserva (dono ou ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_DA_RESERVA
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
